cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.CY 

The paper discusses the use of deep learning models and adversarial attacks, which are commonly studied in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper focuses on electroencephalogram (EEG) based brain-computer interfaces (BCIs), which falls under the sub-category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
